data.description: Discover the allure of this exquisite residence situated in a sought-after West Valley locale. Adorned with granite countertops, the kitchen boasts dark cabinets crowned with molding. Embrace energy efficiency with features like a programmable thermostat, gas water heater, and a gas range. The convenience extends to a Whirlpool washer and gas dryer. The owner's suite is adorned with a spacious walk-in closet. Enjoy the meticulously landscaped front yard and a covered patio in the backyard. Revel in spectacular mountain views. Located just minutes away from Verrado, this home is nestled in a master-planned community with walking trails, greenbelts, a neighborhood park featuring a playground, soccer field, and volleyball court. Benefit from top-rated schools! See this today!
